              "text": "```javascript\nexport \nfunction hanning(M) {\n    if (M < 1) {\n        return new Float64Array();\n    }\n    if (M === 1) {\n        return new Float64Array([1]);\n    }\n    const denom = M - 1;\n    const factor = Math.PI / denom;\n    const cos_vals = new Float64Array(M);\n    for (let i = 0; i < M; ++i) {\n        const n = 2 * i - denom;\n        cos_vals[i] = 0.5 + 0.5 * Math.cos(factor * n);\n    }\n    return cos_vals;\n}\n```",
